==Yang Metal Dog (庚戌)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 2 or 7 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Jin|ja|壬}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)}}), the month of {{ill|September|ja|9月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Kou-Inu|ja|庚戌}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Cold Dew|ja|寒露}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Winter|ja|立冬}}) as applicable.

