It is the 47th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|己酉|lt=Kiyuu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Shingai|ja|辛亥|lt=Shingai|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|金|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Dog|ja|戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (Earth generates Metal).

